title: StarTalk Live! SF Sketchfest
description:
Where did we come from? Are we alone? Explore these questions with guest host Bill Nye the Science Guy, co-host Eugene Mirman and their guests comedian Dave Foley and SETI Institute Sr. Astronomer Seth Shostak.
(Warning: Since this show was recorded live before an adult audience in San Francisco, be prepared for some suggestive language and humor.)
Read more and listen to the full track: http://www.startalkradio.net/show/startalk-live-sf-sketchfest/
author: feed@startalkradio.net (Neil deGrasse Tyson)
